Categorisation copy fields:

text_gen field is used by the taxonomy team as default. The fields below are used ad hoc in
category queries.

textnocasnopunc (not case sensitive, punctuation removed)
textcasnopunc (case sensitive, punctuation removed)
textcaspunc (case sensitive, punctuation preserved)

